    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 121.015 to define \"executive committee of a political party\"; amend KRS 121.150 to specify that a qualified political party committee, including a state or county executive committee, may endorse, support, oppose, and make contributions or expenditures to nonpartisan candidates."
